(8) One member representing small business with
113 knowledge and expertise in risk and resilience.
114 (9) One member representing the broadband and
115 telecommunications industry.
116 (10) One member representing public utilities regulated
117 by the Alabama Public Service Commission.
118 (11) Additional nonvoting members may be appointed to
